text: Ærest on Uþing ford.
Of ðæs cumbes heafode on ðone smalan weg þurh þone more to wiðig slede þæt to brocenan beorge.
Swa to wudu forda.
<../images/tbar.gif>to Lulles beorge.
Swa forð andlang hærpaðæs to Mægenstanes dæne.
Swa to wiðig leagate.
Þæt to næddran beorge.
Þæt þurh ðone mor bæriht gemære on wiðig mor.
Ðæt æft on Ucing ford.
Ærest of sæ upp on Hængestes ricg.
Þonan norð on gyrd weg.
Swa norð andlang rihges on middeweardna sealtera cumb.
<../images/tbar.gif>bæ cumbæ ingon holan broc.
Þonne andlang streames in on hlosmoc.
Adune on stream on seofan æceras.
Þær of streame æft on butan seofan æceras.
Æft suð on hlosmoc.
Ðæt a dune on stream of ða suran apældran.
Ðæt suð on þa norð rewe.
Ðanan eft ofer Cærn on gata forð.
Ðet suð bufan litlan graf swa suð on earnes hlinc.
Of earnes hlince æft utt on sæ.
